Description of 
Holotype

. Body long and slender, widest at temporal region, slightly tapering to groin; head comparatively small (HL/SUL 
0.33
, HW/SUL 
0.30
), not wider than trunk, longer than wide (HL/HW 
1.10
); snout long (SL/HL 
0.44
